tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE error_correction_history (
    history_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    error_id INT,
    correction_date DATE,
    correction_successful BOOLEAN,
    FOREIGN KEY (error_id) REFERENCES quantum_error_correction_metadata(error_id)
);

CREATE TABLE error_correction_metrics (
  metric_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  error_rate DECIMAL,
  correction_rate DECIMAL,
  correction_accuracy DECIMAL
)

CREATE TABLE error_logs (
  log_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  error_type VARCHAR(50),
  error_description TEXT
)

CREATE TABLE error_sources (
  source_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  source_name VARCHAR(50),
  source_description TEXT
)

CREATE TABLE error_corrections (
  correction_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  correction_method VARCHAR(50),
  correction_details TEXT
)
